'''Glydus Mining Corporation''' was a [[Duros/Legends|Duros]]-run mining corporation that owned the [[Glydus Mining Platform]] on [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. They were later consumed by [[DuroDelve Industries]] after going bankrupt shortly before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].<ref name="University">{{GamerCite|2|The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life: The Duros}}</ref>

